        "action": "Change the law to ban local councils from using schools as polling stations.",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "The school my children attend is regularly closed to allow the local council to use it as a polling station. It is not acceptable to allow this to continue happening.  Education is being interrupted, this does not set a good example to children or parents when the government allows this to happen.",
